00:56:46.480 --> 00:56:47.270
AUDIENCE: I got a mike.

00:56:47.270 --> 00:56:47.490
Hi.

00:56:47.490 --> 00:56:48.448
So thank you very much.

00:56:48.448 --> 00:56:51.530
That was a really great
